Package: mosquitoSIT
Title: Bayesian Inference for Mosquito Diffusion-Capture Models (SIT)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Erico", "Souza", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "erico.souza@student.centralesupelec.fr")
Description: Fits a 2D diffusion-reaction PDE model to mosquito trap capture
    data using Bayesian inference via Stan (HMC/NUTS). Infers diffusion
    coefficient (D), mortality rate (LAMBDA), and trap capture rate (GAMMA).
    Designed for Sterile Insect Technique (SIT) studies.
